{# Bookmark toggle button (task 28.1).
   Validates: Requirements 6.4
   Design: §4.2 (htmx interaction patterns)

   Render-state-only partial. The same fragment is returned by the
   `POST /api/bookmarks/toggle` endpoint so the button swaps in place
   via `hx-swap="outerHTML"`.

   Inputs:
     - jobId        : number               — Job_Posting.id
     - bookmarked   : boolean              — current state
     - csrfToken    : string               — 43-char base64url session
                                             CSRF token (rendered into
                                             hx-headers)
     - locale       : 'id' | 'en' | undef  — used for the icon's
                                             `aria-label` only
   Behaviour:
     - `aria-pressed` reflects the toggle state for assistive tech.
     - `hx-vals` is JSON, NOT a query string, so the POST sends a
       JSON body (`Content-Type: application/json` is added by htmx
       when `hx-ext='json-enc'` is present; without that ext, htmx
       URL-encodes the values, which Fastify's `formbody` parser
       handles fine — both shapes are accepted by the route).
     - `hx-headers` carries the X-CSRF-Token mirror of the cookie so
       the server-side double-submit check (Design §8.6) passes.
     - `hx-swap="outerHTML"` replaces this very `<button>` with the
       fragment the server returns for the new state.
#}
{% set bmTr = {
  id: {
    add: 'Tambahkan ke favorit',
    remove: 'Hapus dari favorit'
  },
  en: {
    add: 'Bookmark this job',
    remove: 'Remove bookmark'
  }
} %}
{% set bmT = bmTr[locale] or bmTr.id %}

<button
  id="bookmark-btn-{{ jobId }}"
  type="button"
  class="bookmark-btn{% if bookmarked %} bookmark-btn--on{% else %} bookmark-btn--off{% endif %}"
  aria-pressed="{% if bookmarked %}true{% else %}false{% endif %}"
  aria-label="{% if bookmarked %}{{ bmT.remove }}{% else %}{{ bmT.add }}{% endif %}"
  data-job-id="{{ jobId }}"
  hx-post="/api/bookmarks/toggle"
  hx-vals='{"jobId": {{ jobId }}}'
  hx-headers='{"X-CSRF-Token": "{{ csrfToken }}"}'
  hx-swap="outerHTML"
>
  {% if bookmarked %}
    <span aria-hidden="true" class="bookmark-icon bookmark-icon--filled">★</span>
  {% else %}
    <span aria-hidden="true" class="bookmark-icon bookmark-icon--outline">☆</span>
  {% endif %}
</button>
